AutonomousA() - Method in class edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.templates.optonomousPrime
First Autonomous Mode: Starts idle, goes forward based on the ultrasonic sensors, raises the arm up, scores, brings arm down, goes backward based on the ultrasonic sensors, collects more balls, goes forward based on the ultrasonic sensors, scores, brings the arm down.Stops.
AutonomousB() - Method in class edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.templates.optonomousPrime
Second Autonomous Mode: Goes backward based on ultrasonic sensors, knocks the balls down, goes forward based on the ultrasonic sensors, raises the arm up, scores, brings the arm down.Stops.

moveToMidPosition() - Method in class edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.templates.BallScorer
When the MIDDLE_BUTTON is pressed and the arm is at the MIDDLE_POS nothing will happen.When the MIDDLE_BUTTON is pressed and the arm is above the MIDDLE_POS the arm will go down, when the arm is below the MIDDLE_POS the arm will go up.
moveToScoringPosition() - Method in class edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.templates.BallScorer
When the SCORING_BUTTON is pressed and the arm is below the top limit switch, the arm will go up until the potentiometer reads the scoring value.When the SCORING_BUTTON is pressed and the arm is at the top limit switch nothing will happen.
